'''喬治·大衛·沃林斯基''' （{{lang-fr|Georges David Wolinski}}，{{bd|1934年|6月28日|2015年|1月7日}}），生於[[突尼斯|突尼斯]]的[[法國|法國]][[猶太|猶太]]裔[[漫畫家|漫畫家]]。於2015年1月7日連同其他《[[查理週刊|查理週刊]]》職員一起[[查理週刊總部槍擊案|遭槍擊]]身亡<ref name=tele-attack-live>{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/france/11329976/Paris-Charlie-Hebdo-attack-live.html |title=Paris Charlie Hebdo attack: live |quote=Famous French cartoonists Cabu, Charb, Tignous and Wolinski all reported killed in the attack. |authors=Andrew Marszal; Barney Henderson; David Millward |accessdate=8 January 2015 |work=The Telegraph |date=8 January 2015 |archive-date=2015-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109194558/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/france/11329976/Paris-Charlie-Hebdo-attack-live.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=【國際突發】法國報社遭槍擊 警方：增至12死 |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20150107/53309780 |publisher=[[蘋果日報|蘋果日報]] |date=2015-01-07 |accessdate=2015-01-10 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304133144/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20150107/53309780 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 生平 ==
=== 早年生活 ===
喬治·沃林斯基於1934年6月28日出生於[[法屬突尼斯|法屬突尼斯]][[突尼斯市|突尼斯市]]<ref name="leparisienattentat">[http://www.leparisien.fr/faits-divers/attentat-a-charlie-hebdo-cabu-charb-tignous-et-wolinski-parmi-les-victimes-07-01-2015-4426073.php Attentat à Charlie Hebdo : Cabu, Charb, Tignous et Wolinski parmi les victimes Charlie Hebdo : Cabu, Charb, Wolinski, Maris et les autres, tués dans l'attaque] {{Wayback|url=http://www.leparisien.fr/faits-divers/attentat-a-charlie-hebdo-cabu-charb-tignous-et-wolinski-parmi-les-victimes-07-01-2015-4426073.php |date=20180708133147 }}, ''[[Le_Parisien|Le Parisien]]'', 7 January 2015</ref><ref name="lefigaroevene">[http://www.evene.fr/celebre/biographie/georges-wolinski-1820.php Georges Wolinski: Illustrateur de BD français] {{Wayback|url=http://www.evene.fr/celebre/biographie/georges-wolinski-1820.php |date=20130706125111 }}, ''Le Figaro''</ref><ref name="ynetnews">[http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4612722,00.html Jewish cartoonist among victims of Paris terror attack] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4612722,00.html |date=20170302081437 }}, ''[[Ynetnews|Ynetnews]]'', 8 January 2015, AFP. Retrieved 8 January 2015</ref>。他的父母洛拉·本伯倫（Lola Bembaron）和齊格飛‧沃林斯基（Siegfried Wolinski）都是[[猶太人|猶太人]]<ref name="ynetnews"/> 。他的父親在[[波蘭|波蘭]]出生，並在沃林斯基2歲的時候被殺害<ref name=bbcob>{{cite news|title=Charlie Hebdo attack: Victim obituaries|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-30724678|accessdate=8 January 2015|work=BBC|date=8 January 2015|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125002859/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-30724678|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而他的母親則是{{link-en|意大利籍突尼斯人|Italian Tunisians}}<ref name="lefigaroevene"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.forward.com/the-arty-semite/149000/getting-to-know-cartoonist-georges-wolinski|title=Getting to Know Cartoonist Georges Wolinski|date=4 January 2012|work=The Jewish Daily Forward|access-date=2015-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150228230128/http://blogs.forward.com/the-arty-semite/149000/getting-to-know-cartoonist-georges-wolinski/|archive-date=2015-02-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>[http://moked.it/blog/2015/01/08/georges-wolinski-1934-2015/ Moked - il portale dell´ebraismo italiano - Georges Wolinski] {{Wayback|url=http://moked.it/blog/2015/01/08/georges-wolinski-1934-2015/ |date=20190917204859 }} {{it}}</ref>。他們一家在1945年[[二戰|二戰]]結束後不久搬到了法國<ref name="leparisienattentat"/><ref name="ynetnews"/>。沃林斯基在巴黎學習[[建築學|建築學]]，在畢業之後，他開始學習繪畫漫畫<ref>{{cite news|author=Lucy Cormack|title=Charlie Hebdo: Daughter's Instagram post a reminder of the people behind the pencil|url=http://www.smh.com.au/world/charlie-hebdo-daughters-instagram-post-a-reminder-of-the-people-behind-the-pencil-20150108-12jzm8.html|accessdate=8 January 2015|work=The Sydney Morning Herald|date=8 January 2015|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622193152/https://www.smh.com.au/world/charlie-hebdo-daughters-instagram-post-a-reminder-of-the-people-behind-the-pencil-20150108-12jzm8.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

